===============================================================================
                      The festopt_hts_engine version 1.01
                           release December 25, 2010


The festopt_hts_engine is a HMM-based speech synthesis module. It has been
being developed by the HTS working group (see "Who we are" below) and some
graduate students in Nagoya Institute of Technology (see "AUTHORS" in the same
directory).

